    <svcproc svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>QUICK RELEASE VALVE</title>
        <para>If the quick release valve (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400235">Figure 35</hotlnk>) fails to operate properly, it may be repaired as follows:
            Disassemble valve. Inspect valve body, valve seat and spring (if used) for evidence of faulty operation.
            Replace faulty parts, then reassemble valve.
        </para>
